general_provisions.title: General provisions
general_provisions.text1: Staking is carried out on the EcoForce platform and allows users to freeze TRX tokens to receive energy and income.
general_provisions.text2: Participation in staking is voluntary, and the user is responsible for understanding the associated risks.
general_provisions.text3: Staking is regulated by these terms and conditions, which the user accepts when adding tokens to staking.

staking_procedure.title: Staking procedure
staking_procedure.text1: The user adds TRX tokens to staking through their personal account on the platform.
staking_procedure.text2: Frozen TRX tokens automatically participate in the platform's general staking pool.
staking_procedure.text3: Energy is accrued dynamically and calculated based on the total amount of TRX staked on the Tron network.
